title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 10 2022

description:
What Eric Trump says the FBI did at Mar-a-Lago, including rifling through Melania's closet. Were they looking for one of those giant letters Kim Jong-un sent Trump? Tone-deaf Joe Scarborough of MSNBC says Trump is destroying the GOP, truth is just the opposite, the raid on Mar-a-Lago fired up the Trump Train for 2024. Biden officially ends Remain in Mexico policy, while Mayor Eric Adams fumes over illegals bussed to NYC by Texas Governor Abbott. It's outrageous: Washington, D.C. and New Orleans mandate covid shots for public school kids.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
